                                        description='Generate the tab-\
                                        delimited input table.')
SUBPARSER_INPUT.add_argument('-i', '--isolate_names', help='Path to file \
                             containing isolate names or IDs, one per line.  \
                             Default=\'isolates.txt\'. Each line contains an \
